The enthusiastic invoice manufacturers were also not informed that the travel agency chosen in Budapest exclusively organizes trips abroad, so that in the cash payment bill they foolishly indicated as a service a trip within Hungary, which also did not coincide with the practice of issuing invoices of the agency.
